## Get the game

- Download: [https://gog.com/downloads/system_shock_classic/en1installer1](https://gog.com/downloads/system_shock_classic/en1installer1)
- Store page: [https://gog.com/en/game/system_shock_enhanced_edition](https://gog.com/en/game/system_shock_enhanced_edition)

## Extract game assets

- Download extractor: [https://macsourceports.com/utility/extractor](https://macsourceports.com/utility/extractor)
- `mkdir -p "~/Library/Application Support/systemshock/res"`
- Copy extracted `DATA` and `SOUND` directories to `~/Library/Application Support/systemshock/res`

## Shockolate

- Download: [https://macsourceports.com/game/systemshock](https://macsourceports.com/game/systemshock) (pick software mode)
- Extract and run `Shockolate.app`
